      </nav>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Best 9-Letter Bingo Words in Scrabble — Top Scoring Plays</h1>
      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <time datetime="2026-06-30">June 30, 2026</time><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><span>7 min read</span><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔤</span> Word Finder</a>
      </div>
      <!-- Lead paragraph -->
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Nine-letter bingos are among the most spectacular plays in Scrabble. You use all 7 tiles from your rack plus 2 letters already on the board, earning the 50-point bonus while creating a word that often dominates the board. These plays require deep vocabulary knowledge and sharp board vision — here are the best ones to learn.</p>

      <!-- Stat strip -->
