          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">9</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letters Used</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- h2 sections with visual blocks -->
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Top 9-Letter Bingos by Base Score</h2>

      <p class="text-gray-300">These words have the highest raw tile values before premium squares. When you land one on a Triple Word Score, the results are devastating for your opponent.</p>

      <!-- Use hero card for top item -->
