        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Meaning "odd or questioning." With two Z tiles and the Q, this is the king of 9-letter bingos. The 50-point bonus brings it to 88 points minimum — and premium squares can push it past 150.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card grid -->
      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🏷️ EXORCIZED — 28pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">E(1)+X(8)+O(1)+R(1)+C(3)+I(1)+Z(10)+E(1)+D(2) · X + Z power combo</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🏷️ CUSTOMIZE — 23pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">C(3)+U(1)+S(1)+T(1)+O(1)+M(3)+I(1)+Z(10)+E(1) · Common tiles + Z</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🏷️ VULCANIZE — 23pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">V(4)+U(1)+L(1)+C(3)+A(1)+N(1)+I(1)+Z(10)+E(1) · V adds extra value</p></div>
