<p>Whether you're preparing for tournament play or just want to beat your family at game night, the words on this page give you a competitive edge that compounds over time.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Quick Tips</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
